article_title: DFW Obamacare shoppers see more options, modest premium increases
article_text:
Healthcare premiums for DFW consumers on federal marketplace are up 5.1 percent

In Tarrant County, six insurers offer 63 plans, four more than last year

Tax penalties increasing for those who don’t carry health insurance

article_metadata.title: DFW Obamacare shoppers see more options, modest premium increases | The Star-Telegram

og.description: Open enrollment has started for the third year of the health insurance marketplace in Texas and several changes are in store that could affect your pocketbook.
